The Shoprite group recently donated a R5000 voucher to Sisonke South Afrika NPC to purchase groceries for 20 needy families in eNkanini, Joza, Ext 8, 9 and 10. From left: Sisonke South Africa co-founders, Anele Mahlakahlaka (left) and Ndumiso Mahlakahlaka (right) receive the R5000 voucher from the Makhanda Shoprite manager. 